import pyautogui
import time

try:
    pyautogui.hotkey('win', 'r')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    pyautogui.typewrite('notepad')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)
    pyautogui.typewrite('hello habiba')
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED:", e)
